34
00:03:27,205 --> 00:03:29,705
Aku menginginkannya, aku sangat menginginkannya!

35
00:03:29,705 --> 00:03:33,405
-Ada Laser Police juga! -Dan? Bagaimana?

36
00:03:33,405 --> 00:03:34,505
Kuharap ibuku bisa membelikannya...

37
00:03:34,505 --> 00:03:38,005
Kau melanggar janjimu, meminum penawarnya,

38
00:03:38,005 --> 00:03:40,405
