40
00:03:43,505 --> 00:03:48,305
Oh, ya, terima kasih untuk obat cadangannya.

41
00:03:48,305 --> 00:03:51,805
Jangan bilang kalau kau terbawa suasana

42
00:03:51,805 --> 00:03:53,805
